name: Experiment Or Die #88
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Day 6 in The Cool Alphabet is another important letter, N, and specifically N is for Nintendo. There were a a BUNCH of kids in our neighborhood who all went to the same school and who were all around the same age. And people gravitated towards the people that had some kinda perk: nice pool, big yard...Nintendo! I would play for hours at my friends house until I had to leave for dinner. I had to wait for the Playstation before i could buy my own console. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
